   |     +--------------+    +----------------------------------+  |
   |     | Compute Node |--->| Nova Compute + Neutron Agent     |  |
   |     |              |    | Libvirt/QEMU + OVS/Bridge        |  |
   |     +--------------+    +----------------------------------+  |
   |     +--------------+    +----------------------------------+  |
   |     | Storage Node |--->| Cinder Volume / Ceph OSD         |  |
   |     +--------------+    +----------------------------------+  |
   |                                                              |
   +--------------------------------------------------------------+
   
example: OpenStack Architecture Diagram (3 Controller + 2 Compute)
